{"tid":242001,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪痴撚線...","createTime":"2017-05-13T14:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-14T01:36:46.000Z","uid":23552,"like":6,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c954b9fb24872ac9e1deb219297e6a1c14f165b3","tid":242001,"uid":23552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T14:55:48.000Z","msg":"有個男仔朋友約我頭先出嚟食飯行街 之後我應承咗佢 一路行街嘅時候都好地地 有講有笑 到食飯埋單果陣 我唔夠錢比 諗住叫佢比咗先 我陣間出去㩒錢比返佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  之後佢突然間係間餐廳到大叫（全場都聽到） 屌你老母 冇錢學人食飯 你老尾你雞嚟架咋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n痴撚線 我又冇話唔比 洗唔洗咁激動呀 <br />\n<br />\n最後佢都比咗 之後我行去㩒錢比返佢 就諗住走人 唔想見到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n行行下佢捉住我隻手講<br />\n<br />\n頭先買咗飛喎 唔睇埋先走？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我仲點同佢一齊睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後我話唔洗啦 sorry <br />\n<br />\n佢再大叫 屌你老母 屌你老母 <br />\n<br />\n嚇到我急急腳咁走 我真係懷疑佢係咪傻傻地<br />\n<br />\n到依家係咁ws我 say sorry 話頭先衝動咗少少 叫我原諒佢<br />\n<br />\n我依家應該點做？<br />\n<br />\n仲覆唔覆佢好？ 定block咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c3699151b7388b70259729ceb093cd4a32c767","tid":242001,"uid":44323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T14:56:37.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 屌你老母"},{"pid":"faa630b1cccaf30158d8c1d0d2ae7af60e0789b3","tid":242001,"uid":44323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T14:57:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/th